name: Nanobots Eat the Sky
description:
p5js with a painted star scene png as background.

Random walker nanobots both breed and paint over the background.

As each new nanobot is born, they are assigned a random color either from a set of 'organic' tones of red (#522529), yellow (#fbd17e), green (#436c3d), blue (#145879), white or black.

The nanobots will eventually fill the screen although this will take time as they swarm in one spot and do stop breeding once their population reaches 5000.
